{"id": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid__a2-late-chunking__0004", "text": "The demand for care continues to increase because the number of vulnerable elderly people is increasing. Healthcare will therefore grow in 2025 and 2026. Innovation is necessary to meet the rising demand for healthcare. The trade situation with the United States hinders the investment climate necessary for healthcare innovation. In this video, sector analyst Nehreen Al-Mahmoedi explains in 2 minutes what consequences the trade war has for the healthcare sector and what you can do as an entrepreneur.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid__a2-late-chunking__0004", "source_slug": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid", "source_title": "What can the healthcare sector expect in times of geopolitical uncertainty?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/healthcare/wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid.html", "source_date": "2025-08-14", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 4, "n_chunks_total": 19, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 4}}
