{"id": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid__a2-late-chunking__0008", "text": "## Uncertainty inhibits the innovation that is needed", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid__a2-late-chunking__0008", "source_slug": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid", "source_title": "What can the healthcare sector expect in times of geopolitical uncertainty?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/healthcare/wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid.html", "source_date": "2025-08-14", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 8, "n_chunks_total": 19, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 8}}
{"id": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid__a2-late-chunking__0009", "text": "The growth expectations of the healthcare sector in 2025 and 2026 are explained in the video. Important developments such as staff shortages and increasing demand for care provide an explanation. In addition, the trade war waged by the United States and what this means for the healthcare sector are discussed. It is also important for healthcare institutions to be aware of these developments and to take appropriate steps.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid__a2-late-chunking__0009", "source_slug": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid", "source_title": "What can the healthcare sector expect in times of geopolitical uncertainty?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/healthcare/wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid.html", "source_date": "2025-08-14", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 9, "n_chunks_total": 19, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 9}}
{"id": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid__a2-late-chunking__0010", "text": "This video was recorded for the trade deal between the United States and Europe. As part of the trade deal, the United States imposes a 15 percent tariff on medicines from Europe.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid__a2-late-chunking__0010", "source_slug": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid", "source_title": "What can the healthcare sector expect in times of geopolitical uncertainty?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/healthcare/wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid.html", "source_date": "2025-08-14", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 10, "n_chunks_total": 19, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 10}}
{"id": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid__a2-late-chunking__0011", "text": "Also read the publication [Geopolitical tensions inhibit healthcare innovation](https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/healthcare/geopolitical-spanningen-braken-zorgkennis.html) about our expectations for the healthcare sector and for more information about the possible effects of the United States trade war on Dutch healthcare.", "metadata": {"chunk_id": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid__a2-late-chunking__0011", "source_slug": "wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid", "source_title": "What can the healthcare sector expect in times of geopolitical uncertainty?", "source_url": "https://www.abnamro.nl/nl/zakelijk/insights/sectoren-en-trends/sectorprognoses/healthcare/wat-kan-de-zorgsector-verwachten-in-tijden-van-geopolitieke-onzekerheid.html", "source_date": "2025-08-14", "doc_type": "article", "channel": "website", "content_type": "insight_article", "sector": "sectorprognoses", "topic": "sectoren en trends", "language_original": "nl", "language_embedded": "en", "translation_method": "deep-translator", "translated_with": "deep-translator", "chunker": "a2-late-chunking", "chunk_index": 11, "n_chunks_total": 19, "status": "approved", "date_ingested": "2026-04-30", "requires_late_chunking": true, "source_doc_offset": 11}}
